summary: Adds a cozy but convenient playerhouse just outside Whiterun. Contains everything the seasoned dragonslayer could ever need.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a cozy but convenient playerhouse just outside Whiterun. Contains everything the seasoned dragonslayer could ever need.

Features
- Lots of storage (some of it labeled) both inside and outside
- An outdoor smithy with all crafting tools
- Alchemy and Enchanting lab
- Cooking area
- Working bookshelves with room for over 100 books
- Working displaycases and weapon racks
- 2 mannequins

Known issues.
- Companions may get confused in or around the house due to navmesh issue. As I don't use followers and this was primarily created for personal use, this probably will not be fixed.

Please report bugs and dont hesitate to come with suggestions for improvement and/or future mods.
author: CommanderKei
